{"tid":583553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國信佛A片女星與富翁「父女戀」玩完 物色新男友要睇銀行月結單","createTime":"2018-03-07T05:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:04:55.000Z","uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa7276eb04252fd261c6a2303cb9bf34c5bf8b0","tid":583553,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"【唔係釣金龜喎】 信佛A片女星與富翁「父女戀」玩完 物色新男友要睇銀行月結單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180307/large/1520370095_da4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180307%2Flarge%2F1520370095_da4e.jpg&h=753710aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國成人電影女星農納（Nong Nat）改信佛教後美國富翁結婚，但她說這段婚姻「父女戀」已經告終，正開始物色另一位「老細」。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的農納「從良」後，2012與大她約40年的建築業富商內斯蘭（Harold Jennings Nesland）結婚。婚後曾大膽說，擔心房事過激會導致丈夫馬上風。<br />\n這段婚姻並不長久，農納最近承認，去年與內斯蘭分居，拖了一段時間後，對方勉強同意離婚。<br />\n農納說：「我從不需要內斯蘭養我。我不是釣金龜。我亦非走投無路。」她表示，內斯蘭有畀家用，但知道他在美國開銷大，叫他可畀少一點。農納又坦言內斯蘭太老，要人照顧，但她與對方卻分隔兩地。<br />\n<br />\n農納說，對內斯蘭的愛猶如「小孩照顧長者」，現正物色與她生活方式配合的男人。她聲稱裙下之臣數以百計，要精挑細選，<span style=\"color: red;\">有意者須提供全身照、過去五年銀行月結單、離婚證書、國籍等資料。</span><br />\n英國《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"99c58990e29654de1a0f765dcb0fc0172a38fd45","tid":583553,"uid":69794,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8adc838b8bb6374eefaf93c8d771bae79fa1c10","tid":583553,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專業做雞"},{"pid":"06d1729637129b3caef4fcb4233d7c0054627f93","tid":583553,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:19:26.000Z","msg":"有撚"},{"pid":"c2719c946f3fe2e90a18be4b3e365e35aef252b2","tid":583553,"uid":5475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:24:09.000Z","msg":"秦國既女人點睇都覺得有棍"},{"pid":"3589278235c27a3a1cea841f8228f913413f184f","tid":583553,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"做雞都做到咁串"},{"pid":"c1c7e5f9ff2de5a2e092de1961cebc2ecb4d7f7c","tid":583553,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"使唔使影埋碌尻"},{"pid":"24e21d550b2c72ae727e9801fd18bc849ce23e5a","tid":583553,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1d14e01aa0dd04ff2d759aa7f5f0aa3cce6f34","tid":583553,"uid":19360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"信佛A片女星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2c3892d6ff0ddff39b03ab205593b9154f9647","tid":583553,"uid":16904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"拍a片之前副計正d"},{"pid":"5f34d236eca6cf96ef89092b763a2b8e0e83aa96","tid":583553,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"碌鳩呢？"}]}